WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.740
Ky eshte nje kopesht per femije
qe projektuam ne 2007.

00:00:10.111 --> 00:00:14.036
E krijuam kete kopesht
ne forme rrethi.

00:00:14.036 --> 00:00:17.178
Eshte nje lloj qarkullimi pafund
ne maje te catise.

00:00:17.179 --> 00:00:19.699
Nese je prind,

00:00:19.699 --> 00:00:23.663
e di se femijet kane qejf te vijne rrotull.

00:00:24.793 --> 00:00:27.600
Kjo eshte pamja e catise.

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:29.858
Perse e projektuam keshtu?

00:00:29.858 --> 00:00:32.675
Drejtori i kopshtit tha,